{"tid":1967990,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"世界上的 神秘撚 與非神秘撚 的比例","createTime":"2020-04-11T10:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T06:18:16.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef71f1fda4d05c29b0013233d365bbf5597276b","tid":1967990,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"<strong>全球神秘撚數量</strong><br />\n耶穌教 23億<br />\n伊斯蘭 18億<br />\n印度教 11億<br />\n佛教 5億<br />\n民間宗教 4億<br />\n其他宗教 1億<br />\n沒有宗教信仰 12億<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n神秘撚數量 62億<br />\n非神秘撚數量 12億<br />\n<br />\n<strong>諾貝爾得獎者的神秘撚比例</strong><br />\n耶穌教 65%<br />\n猶太教 20%<br />\n其他 4.5%<br />\n沒宗教信仰 10.5%<br />\n<br />\n神秘撚 89.5%<br />\n非神秘撚 10.5%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2017/04/05/christians-remain-worlds-largest-religious-group-but-they-are-declining-in-europe/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Ffact-tank%2F2017%2F04%2F05%2Fchristians-remain-worlds-largest-religious-group-but-they-are-declining-in-europe%2F&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=fe47f844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2017/04/05/christians-remain-worlds-largest-religious-group-but-they-are-declining-in-europe/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_nonreligious_Nobel_laureates\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_nonreligious_Nobel_laureates&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=e76b2b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_nonreligious_Nobel_laureates</a>"},{"pid":"077f376e05c2db3b038329a595594cf624ac997d","tid":1967990,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>全球神秘撚數量</strong><br />\n耶穌教 23億<br />\n伊斯蘭 18億<br />\n印度教 11億<br />\n佛教 5億<br />\n民間宗教 4億<br />\n其他宗教 1億<br />\n沒有宗教信仰 12億<br />\n<br />\n<b